episode: I finished a Lego after I almost quit doing it.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I just finished doing a Lego that was pretty hard

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That's awesome! Feels great to complete a tough build, right?

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Yeah, I was so close to quitting

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Glad you stuck with it! Feels awesome to finish.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Thank you. I feel awesome

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: No problem! You deserve it!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I haven't completed a Lego since  I was a kid

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That's so cool! Feels like being a kid again, right?

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Yeah, I'm trying to feel like a kid again

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That's awesome! Keep it up!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I spend too much time doing adult stuff

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: I get that. Adulting can be overwhelming!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I'm planning on buying more Legos now

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That's awesome! Have fun building!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I'm thinking of buying a bigger one but I'm worried

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: No worries! Go for it!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Yeah, I want to prove it to myself

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: You totally can! Go for it!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: If I can complete this one, I can do any of them

dialogue.speaker: Bot
